{"tid":2176801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共產黨已經開始改寫初中教育","createTime":"2020-08-27T09:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T08:20:56.000Z","uid":207846,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5ccf895d947a7c54cb8f2ed521e2a82ae62d4f68","tid":2176801,"uid":207846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T09:59:19.000Z","msg":"【#香港新課綱：「明瞭《#基本法》」、「確立對國民身份的認同」成香港史教學重心】全文：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2QuYiY1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QuYiY1&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=84119fc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2QuYiY1</a><br />\n<br />\n有別於台灣、中國大陸的教學設計，香港中學的歷史教育一直分為兩科&mdash;&mdash;中國歷史科與歷史科，坊間稱前者為「#中史」，後者為「#西史」。自上世紀50年代，港英政府制訂兩史分家，一路延用至今。兩史分家之下，香港史一直是西史的教學內容，而在中史科較少出現。<br />\n<br />\n新版中史教科書打破了上述做法，自秦代以來，香港的不同史事就貫穿中國歷史的不同篇章。<br />\n<br />\n在舊課綱，香港史被形容為「教學上的參考」，而在23年後的新課綱裏，被界定為「#確立對國民身份的認同」的重要內容。在學習目標一項中，新課綱新增了一點&mdash;&mdash;「了解香港的發展歷程及其與國家發展的關係」，並建議用初中三年10%的課時，教授「#香港發展」：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2QuYiY1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QuYiY1&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=84119fc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2QuYiY1</a><br />\n<br />\n圖：端傳媒設計部<br />\n<br />\n#延伸閱讀<br />\nThe party is over，同窗好友的移民故事 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/31f9iPo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F31f9iPo&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=d86c9c7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/31f9iPo</a><br />\n戴耀廷解僱風暴：特首與建制之手如何伸入港大？<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3afAdNW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3afAdNW&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=9e481533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3afAdNW</a><br />\n中國歷史在香港中學怎麼教？六十年來平行運轉的兩套歷史觀  <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2qicWW1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2qicWW1&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=3dc71d7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2qicWW1</a><br />\n<br />\n【#香港新課綱：「國家」詞頻增加一倍，「公民」、「品德」減少十倍以上】全文：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2QuYiY1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QuYiY1&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=84119fc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2QuYiY1</a><br />\n<br />\n整體對比香港新舊課綱，1997年新課綱的行文之間，強調「公民」及「德育」意識，但2019年新課綱裡相關字詞大幅下降，「國家」的字詞出現次數翻倍。<br />\n<br />\n例如，舊課綱建議教學內容時，會列出公民及德育教育的事例舉隅&mdash;&mdash;當老師教及「秦朝焚書坑儒」，便可以教學生「#尊重言論自由」；讀到東漢士人力斥弄權宦官和外戚的時候，學生應該學習到「#不畏強權」的情操；孫中山事蹟裡則有「#公爾忘私的精神」。<br />\n<br />\n相較之下，新課綱沒有再羅列學生要從中史學習到公民及德育精神，而更著重「國家」的概念。端傳媒統計發現，「國家」這一詞頻在新課綱中新增了一倍至35次，在舊課綱出現較多的「公民」和「品德」詞頻則都大幅下降：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2QuYiY1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QuYiY1&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=84119fc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2QuYiY1</a><br />\n<br />\n圖：端傳媒設計部<br />\n<br />\n#延伸閱讀<br />\nThe party is over，同窗好友的移民故事 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/31f9iPo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F31f9iPo&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=d86c9c7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/31f9iPo</a><br />\n戴耀廷解僱風暴：特首與建制之手如何伸入港大？<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3afAdNW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3afAdNW&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=9e481533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3afAdNW</a><br />\n中國歷史在香港中學怎麼教？六十年來平行運轉的兩套歷史觀  <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2qicWW1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2qicWW1&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=3dc71d7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2qicWW1</a><br />\n<br />\n😽用你選擇的媒體，決定你看見的世界 #加入會員：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2wVfM6g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2wVfM6g&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=4ae8c41b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2wVfM6g</a><br />\n😽小端也有玩推特，歡迎關注我們：@initiumnews<br />\n<br />\n#端傳媒 #中史科 #香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8LzdaVW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8LzdaVW.jpg&h=a4f8e748&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RSHBS9i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSHBS9i.jpg&h=80c57125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JobCCAZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJobCCAZ.jpg&h=1cf25f49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3068d1e1b8c91ed62d4d6d73df2079ce25da5df1","tid":2176801,"uid":207846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T09:59:46.000Z","msg":"【初中中史新課程中，#香港史 擔當了多大的角色？】全文：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2QuYiY1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QuYiY1&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=84119fc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2QuYiY1</a><br />\n<br />\n自上世紀50年代，港英政府制訂兩史分家，一路延用至今。兩史分家之下，香港史一直是西史的教學內容，而在中史科較少出現。<br />\n<br />\n在舊課綱，香港史被形容為「教學上的參考」，而在23年後的新課綱裏，被界定為「確立對國民身份的認同」的重要內容，並建議初中中史課程要用三年10%的課時教授「香港發展」。<br />\n<br />\n任職中史教師20多年的陳仁啟形容「其實在鴉片戰爭之前，香港的歷史沒有什麼可以說的，所以它怎樣做呢？就是秦朝有南征百越，而香港是百越的其中一部分。這個做法剛好能夠回應《基本法》序言。」<br />\n<br />\n圖：端傳媒設計部<br />\n<br />\n#延伸閱讀<br />\nThe party is over，同窗好友的移民故事👉<a href=\"https://bit.ly/31f9iPo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F31f9iPo&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=d86c9c7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/31f9iPo</a><br />\n戴耀廷解僱風暴：特首與建制之手如何伸入港大？👉<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3afAdNW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3afAdNW&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=9e481533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3afAdNW</a><br />\n中國歷史在香港中學怎麼教？六十年來平行運轉的兩套歷史觀👉 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2qicWW1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2qicWW1&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=3dc71d7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2qicWW1</a><br />\n😽用你選擇的媒體，決定你看見的世界 #加入會員：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2wVfM6g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2wVfM6g&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=4ae8c41b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2wVfM6g</a><br />\n😽小端也有玩推特，歡迎關注我們：@initiumnews<br />\n#端傳媒 #中史科 #香港"},{"pid":"83e188a2d47545d604dc94e42c1cf928d574551e","tid":2176801,"uid":207846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:00:30.000Z","msg":"【唐朝曾派兵駐守屯門=解放軍在港駐軍是「其來有自，有歷史根據」？】全文：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2QuYiY1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QuYiY1&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=84119fc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2QuYiY1</a><br />\n<br />\n在學習目標一項中，初中中史科新課綱新增了一點&mdash;&mdash;「了解香港的發展歷程及其與國家發展的關係」，並建議用初中三年10%的課時，教授「香港發展」。<br />\n<br />\n為配合此指引，教材之一的《亮點中國史》作岀了改動。<br />\n<br />\n在其講述唐朝對外海路交通的部分，有三版提到「屯門鎮是當時中外海路交通的重要樞紐」，「唐政府派數以千計的士兵駐守屯門」，一旁則指出「駐軍是國家主權的象徵」，唐代之後，宋、元各朝都有在香港設防，而「基本法第14條列明，中國政府在香港駐軍，也可算是其來有自，有歷史的根據」。<br />\n<br />\n而在舊書中，唐代在屯門駐軍的內容也是附錄內容，但並未有提到《基本法》。<br />\n <br />\n圖：端傳媒設計部<br />\n<br />\n#延伸閱讀<br />\nThe party is over，同窗好友的移民故事👉<a href=\"https://bit.ly/31f9iPo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F31f9iPo&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=d86c9c7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/31f9iPo</a><br />\n戴耀廷解僱風暴：特首與建制之手如何伸入港大？👉<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3afAdNW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3afAdNW&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=9e481533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3afAdNW</a><br />\n中國歷史在香港中學怎麼教？六十年來平行運轉的兩套歷史觀👉 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2qicWW1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2qicWW1&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=3dc71d7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2qicWW1</a><br />\n😽用你選擇的媒體，決定你看見的世界 #加入會員：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2wVfM6g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2wVfM6g&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=4ae8c41b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2wVfM6g</a><br />\n😽小端也有玩推特，歡迎關注我們：@initiumnews<br />\n#端傳媒 #中史科 #香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rGD14gs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrGD14gs.jpg&h=3f0514cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c7b739a076c5760062882f88526f8a7eb53501e","tid":2176801,"uid":207846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cf824b0c0a5746478d73af245087b6d321607c","tid":2176801,"uid":207846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7deee072bc00e07cceb4dc09cc0d8307cb4f35","tid":2176801,"uid":207846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6fa9ba1c703c2690202bd6fcc228f6a5c60d490","tid":2176801,"uid":207846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:12:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aafc641d942d64af4f65b49db6048c05d7417171","tid":2176801,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be7bfcba247faed9d03148375a58185eaf0547c","tid":2176801,"uid":244240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:10:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5fafef579617d6df69e8ed1f68c3ecb6bbe816e1","tid":2176801,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5610c0437decde34e6fda36b6c2f8670aed40428","tid":2176801,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:14:57.000Z","msg":"端傳媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfaa04c478ec97893edc7c3ad91c7bf9ac4fbd7","tid":2176801,"uid":301503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:15:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f2f9dfbeff86c5d62844eb6229918c997fd1ea3","tid":2176801,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T08:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c99f10db4234c670a088688455f07391a6dfce2","tid":2176801,"uid":332804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T08:20:56.000Z","msg":"古代嘅唔同朝代同中共國係冇關係，只要分清呢點就唔會比佢洗腦。"}]}